  "text": "In 2015, Mukai et al. published a report that showed a good therapeutic effect of various endoscopic techniques in 86/89 (96.6%) patients with WOPN and their complication rate was 12.4% (11/89 patients) [CITATION_1] . In our study, the treatment success was achieved in 99/101 (98.02%) patients with a complication rate of 15.84% (16/101).",
